    "body": "Yep it was an effect with randomly generated sparks that could even collide with the ground (from my memory) and it was also used on damaged vehicles but with a smaller amount of sparks.\nI played around with GraionDilach idea and it looks pretty nice!\nThe only problem I found is if the dummy weapon has to have -1 damage to work(every spark heals when it hits the unit), and if you have it on burst it looses sync with the original repair weapon sometimes. It pretty much forced me to make it continuous.\nBut I am going to try and play with it regardless, see if anything breaks during a play-test.\n"
